title: SIP-007 Marketing budget proposal.
body:
Background: 
It's the perfect time now to ramp up our marketing initiatives.  Spartacus has got solid fundamentals and we need to promote Spartacus' strong presence to a broader audience. 

Part of the fund will be used as community task bounties to incentivize contribution to improve product apps and discord automations. 
 
Proposal: 
Allocate $150K from Spartacus DAO to support marketing campaign and community task bounties. 

Please vote to support this proposal.
